WEBVTT

00:12.980 --> 00:14.120
Zhao,

00:14.460 --> 00:15.970
I'm glad

00:16.060 --> 00:17.570
that you're home safe and sound.

00:18.930 --> 00:22.470
(Picturesque Scenery)

00:25.230 --> 00:26.800
You truly have a way with things.

00:27.660 --> 00:29.210
As the Matron of the household,

00:29.300 --> 00:31.280
of course, I'll take care

00:31.430 --> 00:32.960
of the eldest daughter's marriage.

00:34.830 --> 00:37.530
I'll be sure to repay this favor.

00:38.420 --> 00:39.560
Ms. Longevity!

00:40.700 --> 00:42.320
- Zhangru.
- You're finally home.

00:42.870 --> 00:43.729
It was her...

00:43.730 --> 00:44.789
All right, Zhangru.

00:44.790 --> 00:46.340
Let's go and check on Grandmother first.

01:17.190 --> 01:19.960
I've prepared some herbal packs
for Grandmother's usual ailments.

01:20.460 --> 01:21.629
When I'm not here,

01:21.630 --> 01:22.840
just brew them as needed.

01:23.350 --> 01:24.490
All right.

01:26.300 --> 01:27.480
The weather is cold.

01:27.540 --> 01:30.290
Make sure Grandmother's blankets
are extra warm.

01:31.020 --> 01:33.890
Also, burning mugwort is good
for improving circulation too.

01:33.940 --> 01:35.659
Do it regularly during the day.

01:35.660 --> 01:37.170
I'll do that.

01:37.460 --> 01:39.929
By the way, Seventh Uncle brought

01:39.930 --> 01:42.209
a special herbal tonic from the town.

01:42.210 --> 01:44.430
It's said to be excellent for migraines.

01:45.410 --> 01:46.950
Father is thoughtful.

01:51.850 --> 01:52.729
Grandmother.

01:52.730 --> 01:53.870
Grandmother!

01:54.650 --> 01:57.030
Grandmother, you're awake.

01:57.530 --> 01:58.670
Ms. Longevity?

02:00.890 --> 02:02.230
I'm back.

02:02.850 --> 02:04.310
I'm glad that you're home.

02:04.930 --> 02:06.209
I'm so sorry

02:06.210 --> 02:07.750
for making you worry.

02:08.890 --> 02:10.350
Thankfully, it's not serious.

02:10.650 --> 02:12.790
Otherwise, I'd never forgive myself.

02:21.290 --> 02:22.430
Here, slowly.

02:27.330 --> 02:28.750
Don't blame yourself.

02:29.450 --> 02:32.809
That scheming woman
exaggerated everything,

02:32.810 --> 02:34.310
knowing I'd get flustered.

02:34.570 --> 02:37.769
I was muddled by my migraine

02:37.770 --> 02:41.670
and worried something
might happened to you in Futing.

02:42.090 --> 02:43.950
That wretched Wang Yingxue

02:44.090 --> 02:45.649
secretly signed the marriage contract

02:45.650 --> 02:47.230
while Zhao was away in Futing.

02:50.210 --> 02:51.350
Is it with the Wei Family?

02:54.330 --> 02:56.150
Those scoundrels.

02:56.270 --> 02:58.859
I'll go find those two defiant sons
to break off the engagement.

02:58.860 --> 03:00.050
Grandmother,

03:00.850 --> 03:02.470
I've grown up now.

03:02.490 --> 03:03.409
Let me handle

03:03.410 --> 03:05.390
this matter myself.

03:05.490 --> 03:07.870
I'll head to the Capital tomorrow
and settle it.

03:08.290 --> 03:10.430
You just got back,
and now you're leaving again?

03:10.770 --> 03:12.390
Since it can't be avoided,

03:12.690 --> 03:14.590
I'd rather face it head-on.

03:15.330 --> 03:18.270
I can not only solve this
returning to the Capital,

03:18.370 --> 03:19.369
but also

03:19.370 --> 03:21.239
broaden my mind

03:21.240 --> 03:23.080
just as you've always wanted for me.

03:23.810 --> 03:26.390
It'll widen my view there.

03:31.530 --> 03:32.670
Ms. Longevity,

03:33.450 --> 03:36.150
it's my failing health

03:36.690 --> 03:38.310
that I failed to protect you.

03:38.370 --> 03:40.310
Grandmother, don't say that.

03:41.650 --> 03:42.990
Like you've taught me,

03:43.890 --> 03:46.790
we can't always live
under the other's protection.

03:47.450 --> 03:48.670
This time,

03:49.170 --> 03:51.070
let me protect you.

03:53.810 --> 03:55.489
With your wit,

03:55.490 --> 03:58.630
I'm sure you'll handle
everything well in the Capital.

03:58.810 --> 04:00.070
But remember,

04:00.970 --> 04:02.430
be cautious and know your limit.

04:04.450 --> 04:05.590
Old Madam,

04:05.970 --> 04:07.110
look.

04:10.090 --> 04:10.939
Grandmother,

04:10.940 --> 04:12.569
remember when Ms. Longevity and I tried

04:12.570 --> 04:14.209
to make lotus root dumplings

04:14.210 --> 04:15.350
for you when we were kids?

04:16.930 --> 04:19.110
The moment you two put them into a pot,

04:19.130 --> 04:21.790
the fillings fell apart.

04:22.450 --> 04:23.569
This time,

04:23.570 --> 04:25.590
we made them for you again.

04:26.130 --> 04:27.310
Please have a taste.

04:28.210 --> 04:29.489
How's the taste?

04:29.490 --> 04:30.630
Try it.

04:31.930 --> 04:33.070
Give one to me.

04:36.250 --> 04:38.050
They didn't break apart
this time, right?

04:39.650 --> 04:40.790
Is it good?

04:42.330 --> 04:43.470
Yes, it is.

04:45.650 --> 04:46.790
Fourth Young Lady,

04:46.970 --> 04:49.430
these are clothes preferred
by the Capital's noble ladies.

04:49.490 --> 04:51.910
Fifth Master insists
you change into them.

04:54.490 --> 04:55.710
I'll take my leave.

04:57.450 --> 05:00.439
He just doesn't want you
showing up in plain clothes

05:00.440 --> 05:02.390
and embarrassing him in the Capital.

05:06.040 --> 05:08.290
Your birthday is coming up.

05:08.400 --> 05:10.760
In previous years,
we've always listened

05:10.770 --> 05:12.410
to "Plum Blossoms at Ge Creek" together.

05:12.420 --> 05:14.710
But it seems we won't get
to celebrate together this year.

05:22.010 --> 05:23.430
Why is there music?

05:40.330 --> 05:42.150
Maybe it's a passing musician playing

05:42.250 --> 05:43.870
for their own pleasure.

05:56.970 --> 05:58.670
Let this tune

05:59.530 --> 06:03.230
be our celebration for my birthday.

06:03.490 --> 06:06.870
This song reminds us not
to waste our youth.

06:07.450 --> 06:08.830
You've said

06:09.770 --> 06:11.950
that you've been confined here
the whole life.

06:12.330 --> 06:14.350
You never get
to see the great world outside.

06:14.570 --> 06:16.630
Once I've taken care of things
in the Capital,

06:16.850 --> 06:18.950
we'll make the wish come true.

06:19.610 --> 06:22.910
We'll row a boat, pick flowers, and travel
across the rivers and mountains together.

06:23.530 --> 06:24.830
Take me too.

06:24.850 --> 06:26.630
You cannot leave me out.

06:27.890 --> 06:28.889
Here.

06:28.890 --> 06:30.489
Grandmother, Zhangru.

06:30.490 --> 06:31.750
Promise

06:32.100 --> 06:33.240
to wait for my return.

06:34.550 --> 06:35.690
- Promise.
- I will.

07:58.370 --> 08:02.569
=Blossom=
(Adapted from the novel "Blossom" by Zhi Zhi)

08:02.570 --> 08:05.830
=Episode 12=

08:06.210 --> 08:09.510
(Serene Horizons)

08:22.370 --> 08:23.870
Aren't you going to show yourself?

08:34.850 --> 08:36.750
A man broke into the courtyard
on a quiet night.

08:38.530 --> 08:39.750
Why aren't you afraid?

08:40.290 --> 08:42.670
I wasn't afraid
because I knew it was you.

08:49.900 --> 08:51.390
Thank you for the song you played

08:52.000 --> 08:54.110
and the protection you provided
along the way.

08:56.890 --> 08:58.550
I only intended to stay hidden,

08:59.210 --> 09:00.430
not disturb you.

09:02.410 --> 09:04.150
It's rare for you to listen to me.

09:04.250 --> 09:05.590
So it was quite unexpected.

09:06.050 --> 09:07.250
It is also rare to meet a woman

09:07.260 --> 09:09.280
who understands the situation
as clearly as you do.

09:09.290 --> 09:10.550
You're the most insightful woman

09:13.370 --> 09:15.270
I've ever met.

09:20.360 --> 09:22.550
I'm not as insightful as you think.

09:23.290 --> 09:24.910
The troubles at home weigh on me.

09:26.250 --> 09:28.630
Yet I lack the courage to deal
with them decisively.

09:29.370 --> 09:30.369
At best, I'm someone

09:30.370 --> 09:32.430
who can help others but not myself.

09:33.610 --> 09:34.750
That's why

09:35.090 --> 09:37.510
I've decided to learn
from your decisiveness

09:37.930 --> 09:40.150
and return to the Capital
to handle my family affairs.

09:40.730 --> 09:42.240
Instead of being controlled by others,

09:42.250 --> 09:43.590
I should take the initiative.

09:43.730 --> 09:44.689
Good.

09:44.690 --> 09:47.870
Then I wish you success
in overcoming all obstacles.

09:48.090 --> 09:49.230
Thank you.

09:50.850 --> 09:52.150
Surely

09:52.250 --> 09:53.569
you didn't come all this way

09:53.570 --> 09:54.790
just to flatter me?

09:56.210 --> 09:57.550
I came to say goodbye.

09:58.330 --> 10:00.510
I'm leaving for Liaodong tonight

10:00.570 --> 10:02.110
and won't return for some time.

10:02.530 --> 10:03.670
Before I set out,

10:04.930 --> 10:06.110
I want to return this to you.

10:15.870 --> 10:19.200
♪Riding across the desolate battlefield
in the wind♪

10:19.590 --> 10:22.780
♪The turbulence unfolding
one after another♪

10:23.850 --> 10:26.529
♪The lingering uncertainty
has yet been resolved♪

10:26.530 --> 10:27.830
If you need help,

10:28.770 --> 10:30.150
send someone to find me.

10:30.980 --> 10:33.649
♪The world is vast and turbulent♪

10:33.650 --> 10:35.310
I appreciate the thought.

10:36.090 --> 10:38.310
But I want to handle these myself.

10:39.470 --> 10:43.449
♪When the time comes,
all pride will be laid down♪

10:43.450 --> 10:44.630
What is this flower?

10:44.890 --> 10:46.710
You seem to cherish it a lot.

10:47.150 --> 10:48.449
It's called purple crape myrtle,

10:48.450 --> 10:49.630
a type of wildflower.

10:56.650 --> 10:58.190
You need not worry.

10:58.810 --> 11:00.590
These flowers can endure
countless storms

11:00.650 --> 11:01.990
and grow strong on their own.

11:02.810 --> 11:04.590
I believe they can.

11:05.050 --> 11:06.310
But I also believe

11:06.970 --> 11:09.750
a little help can make it grow faster.

11:15.850 --> 11:18.390
(Duke of Ying's Residence)

11:20.850 --> 11:22.710
So this is how chess is played?

11:22.930 --> 11:24.150
Thank you for the lesson, sir.

11:26.350 --> 11:28.000
- Look at this.
- Then this move is...

11:33.930 --> 11:35.449
Why are there suddenly

11:35.450 --> 11:37.310
so many unfamiliar servants around?

11:37.530 --> 11:39.169
There's been a lot of work these days,

11:39.170 --> 11:40.310
so they hired new servants.

11:40.690 --> 11:41.669
Where's Lu Zheng?

11:41.670 --> 11:43.689
It seems the Duke
has assigned him a task.

11:43.690 --> 11:44.930
I haven't seen him for a while.

11:50.290 --> 11:51.139
Put these away.

11:51.140 --> 11:52.550
- Put it away.
- Yes.

11:57.210 --> 11:59.550
Madam is seriously ill,
so she has no appetite.

11:59.570 --> 12:01.849
Why bring these greasy foods
that make her vomit blood?

12:01.850 --> 12:03.169
Are you trying to get her killed?

12:03.170 --> 12:05.110
I was only assigned
to Madam's room today.

12:05.570 --> 12:07.110
I didn't know her dietary restrictions.

12:15.850 --> 12:17.630
How is she doing now?

12:21.070 --> 12:22.809
Madam doesn't like
the new bitter medicine.

12:22.810 --> 12:25.750
The kitchen is preparing
her favorite preserved fruits right now.

12:41.850 --> 12:44.529
This girl willingly admits her mistakes
and returns to the Capital.

12:44.530 --> 12:46.529
I'm sure she has many schemes lined up.

12:46.530 --> 12:48.190
Madam, you must be careful.

12:50.890 --> 12:52.369
Why didn't you inform me

12:52.370 --> 12:54.430
that you were coming back?

12:54.650 --> 12:57.190
Then we could've been better prepared.

12:57.290 --> 12:59.830
I thought you and your mother
had planned this in advance.

13:00.250 --> 13:01.510
The wedding is approaching.

13:01.730 --> 13:03.730
So I need to come back to prepare.

13:04.170 --> 13:05.409
It was you

13:05.410 --> 13:07.150
who found me such a good match,
after all.

13:08.250 --> 13:09.569
This is also Fifth Uncle's wish.

13:09.570 --> 13:10.889
We're family, to begin with.

13:10.890 --> 13:12.409
You should have come back long ago.

13:12.410 --> 13:13.940
I'm glad you've come to terms with it.

13:14.170 --> 13:15.310
That's right.

13:15.370 --> 13:17.529
After all, we are family.

13:17.530 --> 13:19.950
You've been living away from home
for so long.

13:19.970 --> 13:22.710
It might take you some time to adjust.

13:23.050 --> 13:24.169
She'll get used to it.

13:24.170 --> 13:25.310
It doesn't matter.

13:26.570 --> 13:27.889
Don't just stand around.

13:27.890 --> 13:29.070
Hurry inside the house.

13:29.350 --> 13:30.529
- Gao Sheng.
- Yes, Master.

13:30.530 --> 13:32.089
Tell them to get ready for dinner.

13:32.090 --> 13:33.230
Yes, Master.

13:33.610 --> 13:35.830
Move the things inside.

13:36.770 --> 13:38.230
You're kind and gentle.

13:38.570 --> 13:39.729
If you see me

13:39.730 --> 13:41.670
as a burden,

13:42.170 --> 13:44.230
then I truly have no way out.

13:48.330 --> 13:49.769
Now that you're back,

13:49.770 --> 13:52.110
you'll follow the rules
of this household.

13:52.880 --> 13:55.550
You need to hold in
the wild behavior you developed

13:55.610 --> 13:57.430
while living on the manor.

13:58.130 --> 13:59.830
I was mischievous before.

14:00.130 --> 14:01.750
But now I've realized my mistakes.

14:02.210 --> 14:05.350
From now on, I'll follow your teachings
while I'm in the Capital.

14:07.490 --> 14:08.790
In that case,

14:09.090 --> 14:11.270
you can start by copying scriptures.

14:16.890 --> 14:19.190
Wang Yingxue is truely a wicked woman.

14:19.250 --> 14:20.830
You're just back.

14:20.840 --> 14:22.569
But you have to
copy scriptures every day.

14:22.570 --> 14:24.009
And you have to copy it ten times.

14:24.010 --> 14:26.089
Our life was so carefree
at the manor in Zhending.

14:26.090 --> 14:27.750
Why come to the Capital to suffer?

14:27.950 --> 14:29.729
Fourth Young Lady
doesn't even say a word.

14:29.730 --> 14:31.310
Yet, you're complaining non-stop.

14:31.350 --> 14:32.809
Since you love staying at the manor,

14:32.810 --> 14:34.249
I'll send you back to the manor

14:34.250 --> 14:35.020
to serve Old Madam.

14:35.030 --> 14:36.049
Please don't send me back.

14:36.050 --> 14:37.510
I'll just stop complaining.

14:39.370 --> 14:40.160
Who is it?

14:40.170 --> 14:43.219
Fourth Young Lady, Manager Zhao from
the calligraphy shop asked me to deliver

14:43.220 --> 14:44.990
some new Xuan paper
and an inkstone for you.

14:48.850 --> 14:50.070
He also said

14:50.170 --> 14:52.590
some matters
among the items require your attention.

15:09.770 --> 15:11.849
(The Duchess of Ying is seriously ill.)

15:11.850 --> 15:13.049
(The servants were changed.)
This is from Mr. Chen.

15:13.050 --> 15:14.940
(The heir's close attendants
have gone missing.)

15:16.210 --> 15:19.030
(Most of the servants have served
the family for generations.)

15:19.330 --> 15:21.350
(Why would they suddenly replace
so many of them)

15:21.410 --> 15:23.510
(while the Matron of the house is ill? )

15:24.150 --> 15:26.510
(Song Mo, Star of Doom)
(A strike cuts through the heaven.)

15:26.570 --> 15:28.750
(Discarded after the purpose is served.)

15:29.210 --> 15:31.470
(Blood is spilled
and what remains is resentment.)

15:32.010 --> 15:34.790
(Injustice and hatred fester within
and are hard to erase.)

15:35.090 --> 15:37.790
(Song Mo will kill his father
and brother this year.)

15:38.410 --> 15:41.550
(The upheaval in the Duke of Ying's
Residence is unusual.)

15:42.330 --> 15:45.630
(Could there be another hidden reason
behind his drastic change)

15:45.730 --> 15:47.990
(other than Duke of Ding's injustice?)

15:48.050 --> 15:50.470
(I must have Mr. Chen
look deeper into this.)

15:51.250 --> 15:52.430
Who's there?

15:52.730 --> 15:54.510
Zhao, it's me.

16:02.610 --> 16:03.990
This is steamed bass

16:04.290 --> 16:06.190
and here's the ham
and fresh bamboo shoot soup.

16:06.290 --> 16:09.030
I saw you had a second helping
at the family dinner.

16:09.330 --> 16:10.590
So I thought you might like it.

16:13.130 --> 16:14.390
I made these myself.

16:23.250 --> 16:24.390
The soup is delicious.

16:29.290 --> 16:30.430
Let's eat together.

16:38.050 --> 16:40.400
Your mother punishes me
with scriptures copying, grounds me,

16:40.410 --> 16:41.750
and does not allow visitors.

16:41.970 --> 16:44.150
Aren't you afraid of being punished
for coming here?

16:46.170 --> 16:49.910
It's my fault for being incompetent
and making her upset about everything.

16:50.770 --> 16:52.590
That's why she's keeping
a close eye on you

16:52.600 --> 16:54.540
and worried Father might be partial
toward you.

16:59.450 --> 17:02.230
I've copied
some of the "Lessons for Women" for you.

17:02.890 --> 17:04.710
I also brought some books,

17:04.930 --> 17:06.609
(Annotated Collection of Du Fu's Poems)
stories, and plays

17:06.610 --> 17:08.270
for you to pass the time.

17:08.490 --> 17:09.950
You're new to the Capital.

17:10.170 --> 17:13.249
I know where

17:13.250 --> 17:15.289
all the most popular rouge shops,
fabric stores,

17:15.290 --> 17:16.430
and calligraphy shops are.

17:17.690 --> 17:19.769
We can even rent a boat

17:19.770 --> 17:21.489
to tour the lake

17:21.490 --> 17:23.310
and listen to music while we're at it.

17:25.330 --> 17:26.990
That's something from before I was born.

17:27.050 --> 17:29.110
But I've heard the elders mention it.

17:29.370 --> 17:30.990
How could I know all of that?

17:31.210 --> 17:32.609
After you're no longer grounded,

17:32.610 --> 17:34.270
I'll go with you.

17:38.650 --> 17:43.030
Do you not like touring the lake
and listening to music?

17:43.570 --> 17:44.710
It's not like that.

17:45.850 --> 17:50.670
It's just you're so different

17:50.730 --> 17:52.310
from how you used to be.

17:54.010 --> 17:55.550
How I used to be?

18:02.850 --> 18:03.990
Someone's coming.

18:04.930 --> 18:06.070
Hurry.

18:12.570 --> 18:14.390
Let's stop copying for today.

18:16.370 --> 18:18.950
I'm tired and need to rest.

18:41.770 --> 18:42.910
He left.

18:43.210 --> 18:44.350
He already left.

19:01.890 --> 19:03.590
Then I'll take my leave first.

19:04.050 --> 19:05.630
I won't disturb you anymore.

19:11.490 --> 19:12.339
It's strange.

19:12.340 --> 19:14.510
How did they know
you have to copy scriptures?

19:15.770 --> 19:17.470
This one's from Ming.

19:17.610 --> 19:19.689
It looks like she thinks
the same as the rest.

19:19.690 --> 19:20.830
She is quite thoughtful.

19:25.730 --> 19:27.350
Ming's small script is neat.

19:27.590 --> 19:29.270
Wang Yingxue
will definitely recognize it.

19:29.850 --> 19:31.390
We shouldn't implicate her.

19:31.930 --> 19:33.270
But I appreciate her help.

19:34.610 --> 19:36.150
This one is Mr. Wu's writing.

19:36.610 --> 19:37.459
Can we use this?

19:37.460 --> 19:38.870
(Lessons for Women)

19:39.450 --> 19:40.409
(Fulfill one's duties
in family and society.)

19:40.410 --> 19:42.369
His handwriting is delicate and proper.

19:42.370 --> 19:44.750
The reverse strokes are elegant.

19:46.740 --> 19:49.950
But it looks like a man's handwriting,
doesn't it?

19:50.290 --> 19:51.619
You can tell.

19:51.620 --> 19:53.729
But Wang Yingxue probably won't notice.

19:53.730 --> 19:55.430
Who would check so carefully?

19:57.500 --> 19:58.609
Why is Mr. Ji's handwriting

19:58.610 --> 19:59.909
all crooked?

19:59.910 --> 20:01.609
(Lessons for Women)

20:01.610 --> 20:02.609
(Fulfill one's duties
in family and society.)

20:02.610 --> 20:04.310
Jianming knows I hide
the sharp edge when I write.

20:04.330 --> 20:05.479
I've been writing letters

20:05.480 --> 20:07.670
with my left hand
instead of the right one.

20:08.150 --> 20:09.820
He can almost imitate
my handwriting now.

20:09.830 --> 20:12.030
Does it mean we can use this?

20:13.130 --> 20:14.809
There's also one from Lord Song.

20:14.810 --> 20:16.590
It's crooked, too.

20:18.650 --> 20:20.950
(I owe my wisdom to my mother
and female mentors.)

20:26.190 --> 20:28.659
Wait, he wrote this wrongly.

20:28.660 --> 20:31.529
Look at the "Spring and Autumn Annals."

20:31.530 --> 20:33.510
The "Autumn" character
is missing a stroke.

20:34.650 --> 20:37.710
(Autumn)

20:38.210 --> 20:39.129
Young Lady,

20:39.130 --> 20:40.430
is there something wrong?

20:41.090 --> 20:44.110
This is almost exactly the same
as when I write with my left hand.

20:44.650 --> 20:46.670
I leave out that little stroke
in the "Autumn" character

20:47.860 --> 20:50.790
to avoid using my late mother's name.

20:51.670 --> 20:53.590
(Autumn)
He really knows how to read people.

20:54.210 --> 20:56.510
So, do you think we can use both?

20:56.730 --> 20:58.409
There's no conclusion
after all this deliberation.

20:58.410 --> 21:00.070
In my opinion, both should be kept.

21:06.330 --> 21:09.110
(Perpetual Bloom)

21:13.730 --> 21:16.670
(Liaodong)

21:38.530 --> 21:40.190
The Jiang Clan is brave and admirable.

21:40.420 --> 21:42.350
I've always respected them.

21:43.260 --> 21:45.090
But the imperial decree
has just been issued.

21:45.410 --> 21:48.769
If we give them special treatment now,
we might attract criticism.

21:48.770 --> 21:50.289
(Zhu Youting, Lord Qing)

21:50.290 --> 21:51.830
What do you think, Mr. Ji?

21:54.020 --> 21:55.339
Lord Song is a brave and capable man.

21:55.340 --> 21:56.750
Your Highness values talent.

21:57.290 --> 21:59.470
If Your Lordship could help
His Highness,

21:59.730 --> 22:00.950
it would be a win for both sides,

22:01.130 --> 22:02.430
don't you think?

22:03.050 --> 22:04.590
Lizhen has been causing trouble.

22:04.610 --> 22:06.310
His Highness
has been busy preparing for war.

22:06.930 --> 22:09.590
Lord Song,
with his reputation as a young general,

22:09.650 --> 22:11.230
must be excellent in training.

22:13.770 --> 22:15.529
People of Lizhen grew up on horseback.

22:15.530 --> 22:18.550
So it will undoubtedly
be cavalry battles.

22:19.410 --> 22:20.869
They're not like

22:20.870 --> 22:22.510
these lifeless stationary targets.

22:50.730 --> 22:51.870
Distance is twenty zhang.

22:53.610 --> 22:54.750
Impressive.

22:54.850 --> 22:56.339
The sky is filled
with auspicious clouds,

22:56.340 --> 22:57.510
which is a good omen.

22:57.530 --> 23:00.470
It seems the stars are watching over us,

23:00.530 --> 23:01.830
ensuring the border's safety.

23:06.610 --> 23:08.350
Your great reputation

23:08.490 --> 23:09.830
is truly well-deserved.

23:10.530 --> 23:11.369
Shi Chuan.

23:11.370 --> 23:12.289
Yes, Your Highness.

23:12.290 --> 23:14.430
Send someone to repair
the Jiang Clan's houses.

23:15.050 --> 23:16.049
Take a doctor with you.

23:16.050 --> 23:17.190
Yes, Your Highness.

23:19.650 --> 23:21.470
Yantang, why not stay here

23:21.530 --> 23:22.910
to help train the army for me?

23:23.050 --> 23:24.910
It will also be easier
to take care of the Jiang Clan.

23:25.370 --> 23:27.190
I can ask Father for permission.

23:28.190 --> 23:29.670
Thank you for your kindness,
Your Highness.

23:29.850 --> 23:31.910
But I just received an urgent report
from the Capital

23:31.970 --> 23:33.489
that my mother's condition has worsened.

23:33.490 --> 23:34.630
I'm afraid...

23:34.650 --> 23:35.790
Report!

23:36.710 --> 23:37.569
Your Highness,

23:37.570 --> 23:38.649
Lizhen has attacked again.

23:38.650 --> 23:40.049
The forces are ten times stronger
than usual.

23:40.050 --> 23:42.190
This isn't just a raid this time.

23:42.370 --> 23:44.729
Issue orders to all the divisions
to assemble the troops

23:44.730 --> 23:45.990
and prepare for battle.

23:46.610 --> 23:48.829
Send the military reports
to the court immediately.

23:48.830 --> 23:49.689
Yes, Your Highness.

23:49.690 --> 23:50.830
I'm on my way back to the Capital.

23:50.850 --> 23:52.310
I'll take care of the official report.

23:56.210 --> 23:57.550
I just hope we can have a proper talk

23:58.570 --> 23:59.790
when this is all over.

24:08.530 --> 24:11.830
I supposed
Your Lordship has owed me a favor.

24:14.370 --> 24:16.550
Official Ji, you used me
to flatter His Highness.

24:17.530 --> 24:18.670
Who's owing who here?

24:21.890 --> 24:23.710
I don't think
it's twenty zhang as you said.

24:30.930 --> 24:31.889
Young Lady,

24:31.890 --> 24:34.430
things are critical
at Duke of Ying's Residence.

24:35.130 --> 24:37.030
How can you still focus
on copying scriptures?

24:37.810 --> 24:40.390
Rushing won't help.

24:40.490 --> 24:43.630
What we need most
is a calm and steady mind.

24:50.330 --> 24:51.849
Manager Zhao has sent word

24:51.850 --> 24:54.130
that Lord Song left the palace
after sending the official report.

24:56.970 --> 24:58.110
But...

24:58.130 --> 25:00.430
what if Manager Zhao can't stop him?

25:01.290 --> 25:03.350
(If Zhao Liangbi can't stop Song Mo,)

25:04.050 --> 25:05.990
(we'll have no choice but to go all in.)

25:16.810 --> 25:17.950
Pull!

25:20.570 --> 25:21.710
Your Lordship, please wait!

25:24.770 --> 25:25.849
Are you Fourth Young Lady's man?

25:25.850 --> 25:28.169
That's right. She told me
to stop you no matter what.

25:28.170 --> 25:29.409
She also said things won't end well

25:29.410 --> 25:31.190
if Your Lordship returns home now.

25:31.690 --> 25:32.950
My mother is critically ill at home.

25:33.130 --> 25:34.249
As a son,

25:34.250 --> 25:35.169
I must return.

25:35.170 --> 25:36.019
Move aside.

25:36.020 --> 25:37.170
Your Lordship!

25:39.210 --> 25:40.710
Express my thanks to her.

25:42.530 --> 25:43.670
Your Lordship!

25:46.570 --> 25:50.710
(Funeral. Duke of Ying's Residence)

25:57.170 --> 25:58.049
Young Master,

25:58.050 --> 25:59.950
you've finally come home.

26:00.010 --> 26:01.590
Madam passed away the night before

26:01.650 --> 26:03.529
and we've just finished setting up
the mourning hall.

26:03.530 --> 26:04.670
Young...

26:29.050 --> 26:30.190
Mo,

26:30.450 --> 26:31.590
you've finally returned.

26:34.150 --> 26:35.369
(Virtuous Wife,
Madam Jiang's Memorial Tablet)

26:35.370 --> 26:36.590
Before Mother passed,

26:37.010 --> 26:38.630
she refused to take the medicine
I gave her

26:39.370 --> 26:41.190
and kept calling your name.

26:45.050 --> 26:46.390
It's my fault.

26:48.410 --> 26:49.990
I came back late.

26:53.370 --> 26:54.510
(Mother,)

26:55.610 --> 26:56.830
(I have returned.)

26:57.810 --> 26:59.350
(I'm a bad son.)

27:00.930 --> 27:03.230
I failed as your son.

27:20.290 --> 27:21.430
Young Master,

27:21.650 --> 27:24.910
the Duke has been heartbroken
these past few days

27:25.130 --> 27:26.470
and is desperate to see you.

27:27.770 --> 27:28.910
Mother,

27:30.410 --> 27:31.630
I will be right back.

27:32.130 --> 27:38.230
(Virtuous Wife,
Madam Jiang's Memorial Tablet)

27:50.530 --> 27:51.670
Duke of Ying.

27:52.050 --> 27:53.190
Father.

27:54.410 --> 27:56.110
Every time I see this comb,

27:57.090 --> 27:59.510
it feels like Huisun is still here.

27:59.930 --> 28:03.350
She's just off to admire the flowers

28:03.810 --> 28:06.910
and will return soon.

28:10.010 --> 28:11.089
Father,

28:11.090 --> 28:12.230
I've failed as a son.

28:14.610 --> 28:16.750
I failed to be with Mother
in her final moments.

28:26.010 --> 28:29.470
Take a look at this.

28:30.290 --> 28:31.590
Do you recognize it?

28:37.490 --> 28:38.630
Yes, I do.

28:38.690 --> 28:40.830
This is the mutton fat jade
Grandfather had before he passed.

28:41.330 --> 28:42.470
One for me,

28:42.930 --> 28:44.230
and the other one for Han.

28:44.810 --> 28:46.430
I haven't carry it with me,

28:47.770 --> 28:49.270
so it's been long since I last saw it.

28:50.250 --> 28:51.790
I'm glad you recognize it.

28:55.010 --> 28:56.550
This jade piece

28:57.250 --> 28:59.790
was found on Meirui.

29:01.170 --> 29:02.310
Meirui?

29:04.770 --> 29:06.230
The shoulder width
is one and a half feet.

29:07.010 --> 29:08.630
The maid who served my mother?

29:09.570 --> 29:10.910
How did she get it?

29:11.850 --> 29:13.310
How did she get it?

29:13.930 --> 29:17.790
Why don't you ask her yourself?

29:18.770 --> 29:19.910
Someone, carry her inside.

29:32.930 --> 29:34.070
How did this happen?

29:34.610 --> 29:36.910
Young Master, just admit it.

29:37.370 --> 29:40.470
People have seen you sneaking
around with Meirui.

29:41.050 --> 29:42.190
This jade

29:42.210 --> 29:44.870
must have been your token of love.

29:46.970 --> 29:48.110
Father,

29:48.410 --> 29:49.550
I didn't do it.

29:49.650 --> 29:51.089
After Madam's death,

29:51.090 --> 29:52.870
that girl took her own life.

29:53.250 --> 29:55.510
We thought
it was out of loyalty at first.

29:55.930 --> 29:57.310
But the physician said

29:57.730 --> 29:59.950
she was three months pregnant.

30:00.930 --> 30:03.310
When she died, she was clutching

30:03.730 --> 30:05.630
this very jade.

30:05.970 --> 30:08.070
Three months ago,
you returned to the Capital.

30:08.410 --> 30:10.470
You disappeared every day.

30:11.010 --> 30:12.190
I thought

30:12.410 --> 30:15.070
you were busy handling
your uncle's affairs.

30:15.370 --> 30:20.310
I never imagined
you'd do something disgraceful as this!

30:21.290 --> 30:22.409
Father,

30:22.410 --> 30:23.329
I didn't do it.

30:23.330 --> 30:24.790
Lu Zheng has been here the whole time.

30:25.610 --> 30:27.030
He can clear things up for me.

30:27.370 --> 30:28.510
Also,

30:28.530 --> 30:30.470
the maids and the caregivers
who cared for Mother.

30:30.490 --> 30:32.190
- I'm willing to face...
- You good-for-nothing!

30:32.610 --> 30:34.049
When your mother was gravely ill,

30:34.050 --> 30:35.609
you dared to commit
such disgraceful acts?

30:35.610 --> 30:37.689
How can you even justify yourself?

30:37.690 --> 30:40.569
Lu Zheng has been your trusted attendant
for ten years.

30:40.570 --> 30:42.489
Of course, he'll cover for you.

30:42.490 --> 30:44.430
Let alone those servants!

30:44.650 --> 30:46.470
If your mother knew of this
from the afterlife,

30:46.730 --> 30:48.990
how could she not be heartbroken?

30:49.690 --> 30:50.830
Father.

30:51.050 --> 30:52.230
You must believe me.

30:52.370 --> 30:53.289
I didn't do this.

30:53.290 --> 30:54.550
This is completely untrue.

30:54.770 --> 30:55.969
I must teach you a lesson

30:55.970 --> 30:58.630
for her sake!

31:01.010 --> 31:02.150
Father.

31:02.450 --> 31:03.590
Take this!

31:03.650 --> 31:04.769
Master, stop.

31:04.770 --> 31:05.849
Young Master,

31:05.850 --> 31:08.649
the Duke is angry
because he cares about you.

31:08.650 --> 31:10.129
Stop arguing.

31:10.130 --> 31:11.489
Let him vent first,

31:11.490 --> 31:12.449
then explain yourself.

31:12.450 --> 31:13.689
Enough talk!

31:13.690 --> 31:17.390
Someone! Drag this defiant child out and
punish him according to the family rule!

31:26.610 --> 31:28.129
- So, how did it go?
- He failed to stop him.

31:28.130 --> 31:29.310
Failed...

31:30.370 --> 31:32.369
So, is the gate
at the Duke of Ying's Residence closed?

31:32.370 --> 31:33.510
Yes.

31:35.610 --> 31:38.790
If they were receiving condolences,
why would they close it?

31:39.210 --> 31:40.409
Something's definitely wrong.

31:40.410 --> 31:41.769
You're still grounded.

31:41.770 --> 31:43.070
If that's true,

31:43.090 --> 31:44.830
do we still have to be involved?

31:44.930 --> 31:45.969
We've already done our duty

31:45.970 --> 31:47.710
by warning him.

31:48.010 --> 31:49.150
No.

31:49.850 --> 31:50.990
I want to save him.

31:52.410 --> 31:53.289
Inform Mr. Chen

31:53.290 --> 31:54.630
to make the final move.

32:08.570 --> 32:09.710
(Please,)

32:10.010 --> 32:12.390
(let me take the punishment
in place of my father.)

32:12.570 --> 32:13.790
(It violates no military law)

32:14.010 --> 32:15.510
(and remains loyal and filial!)

32:15.850 --> 32:17.529
The whole court knows

32:17.530 --> 32:18.950
that I have to

32:19.050 --> 32:20.529
rely on my good son.

32:20.530 --> 32:22.550
It's also all thanks
to Jiang Meisun's mercy!

32:23.210 --> 32:25.089
(His Majesty even praised you,)

32:25.090 --> 32:27.350
(saying you have Jiang Meisun's
noble spirit!)

32:27.410 --> 32:29.230
Whose son are you exactly?

32:38.330 --> 32:41.270
(Righteous and Unyielding Spirit)

32:43.850 --> 32:46.510
You gave me life.

32:47.530 --> 32:50.510
If you want it, take it.

32:51.490 --> 32:53.750
If you don't want to see me,

32:55.290 --> 32:58.110
I'll never return to the Capital

32:59.930 --> 33:02.390
or come home.

33:03.330 --> 33:05.230
But at least tell me

33:06.450 --> 33:08.790
why are you treating me like this?

33:09.890 --> 33:11.430
Why?

33:13.410 --> 33:15.950
Why?

33:30.330 --> 33:31.550
Lock him up.

33:32.170 --> 33:33.950
Song Mo's disgraceful conduct

33:34.010 --> 33:35.150
cannot be tolerated.

33:35.650 --> 33:38.510
Tomorrow, invite First Brother
and Third Brother here.

33:38.520 --> 33:40.680
I want to hold a family tribunal
and remove him from the family register.

33:40.690 --> 33:42.150
Then report to His Majesty

33:43.050 --> 33:46.670
to strip Song Mo of his title as heir.

34:30.050 --> 34:31.510
(If your family is still around,)

34:31.730 --> 34:33.350
(why not compromise and give it a try?)

34:33.530 --> 34:35.630
(Like doing something
that brings joy to your parents.)

34:47.450 --> 34:49.190
I see.

34:55.010 --> 34:56.990
I understand it now.

35:17.850 --> 35:18.990
Mother.

35:33.250 --> 35:34.390
Go.

36:28.170 --> 36:29.310
Your Lordship,

36:30.130 --> 36:31.270
are you awake?

36:35.370 --> 36:36.950
His Lordship is awake.

36:37.770 --> 36:39.670
Everything is fine so long he's awake.

36:39.770 --> 36:41.550
Then I'll deal with the other things.

36:44.810 --> 36:45.950
Your Lordship.

36:50.730 --> 36:51.870
Fourth Young Lady,

36:53.090 --> 36:54.350
what is this place?

36:56.330 --> 36:57.910
This is Zhaowen Bookstore.

36:57.970 --> 37:00.649
Good thing
you detained Mr. Chen last time.

37:00.650 --> 37:03.270
Otherwise,
I couldn't have saved you by myself.

37:05.490 --> 37:08.870
Your master is already half-dead.

37:10.370 --> 37:13.910
Tomorrow, the family tribunal
will strip him of everything.

37:14.170 --> 37:16.150
If you still can't see
the situation clearly,

37:16.490 --> 37:18.830
I'll write the confession for you.

37:19.370 --> 37:21.390
All you need to do is sign
with your fingerprint.

37:23.090 --> 37:24.470
Can you even write,

37:24.730 --> 37:25.870
you fool?

37:31.290 --> 37:33.310
(Create diversion
and rescue during the chaos.)

37:33.370 --> 37:35.670
(Meet at the corner gate
and escape to safety.)

37:36.810 --> 37:39.070
Or do you want to go first?

37:41.530 --> 37:42.670
Stop! Stop it!

37:43.370 --> 37:45.230
The Duke wants to drive us
to our deaths?

37:45.650 --> 37:48.030
Then I'll take you all down with me!

37:50.650 --> 37:51.790
Hurry.

37:52.490 --> 37:53.910
This way. Hurry up.

37:55.610 --> 37:56.449
Come on. Hurry.

37:56.450 --> 37:57.630
Young Master has escaped!

37:57.930 --> 37:58.769
This way!

37:58.770 --> 37:59.910
Catch them!

38:04.710 --> 38:05.559
Go now!

38:05.560 --> 38:06.829
- Lu Ming, hurry!
- Leave now!

38:06.830 --> 38:08.090
Get out of here now!

38:25.800 --> 38:26.809
Zheng!

38:26.810 --> 38:27.729
Leave!

38:27.730 --> 38:29.959
Lu Ming, leave now!

38:29.960 --> 38:31.200
Zheng!

38:32.370 --> 38:34.150
Protect His Lordship!

38:39.210 --> 38:40.059
Zheng!

38:40.060 --> 38:42.249
We must leave now!

38:42.250 --> 38:44.469
(Create diversion
and rescue during the chaos.)

38:44.470 --> 38:46.750
(Meet at the corner gate and escape.)

38:48.010 --> 38:50.870
Father and son sit side by side
but do not understand each other.

38:51.810 --> 38:55.550
Strangers risk their lives to save me.

38:58.210 --> 39:01.150
You sneak out in the middle of the night
to meet a man.

39:01.610 --> 39:04.870
Do you know the consequences

39:05.290 --> 39:06.809
if your stepmother
and Fifth Uncle found out?

39:06.810 --> 39:08.110
The situation was urgent.

39:09.290 --> 39:10.710
Since I've already saved you,

39:10.850 --> 39:12.510
I have my ways of handling it.

39:14.330 --> 39:18.150
Besides, you saved me before.

39:21.410 --> 39:22.870
Saved you?

39:25.210 --> 39:26.510
I mean,

39:26.650 --> 39:29.470
you saved me back in Futing.

39:30.370 --> 39:31.790
Now that Mr. Chen has returned,

39:32.170 --> 39:33.550
we no longer owe each other anything.

39:44.050 --> 39:47.710
Your handwriting
isn't as messy as it used to be.

39:48.650 --> 39:50.670
It seems strangely familiar.

39:50.730 --> 39:52.569
(Create diversion
and rescue during the chaos.)

39:52.570 --> 39:56.030
(Allow me to be bold enough
to guess what's on your mind.)

40:02.730 --> 40:04.150
You're avoiding my gaze.

40:05.170 --> 40:06.990
Do you still remember

40:07.610 --> 40:09.310
the incomplete play
of "The Life of Luo Shan"

40:10.410 --> 40:13.110
at Guanghe Tower
during the Tiancang Festival Festival?

40:19.850 --> 40:21.390
You've mistaken me for someone else.

40:22.170 --> 40:23.470
I don't watch plays.

40:28.890 --> 40:30.150
You're heavily injured.

40:30.210 --> 40:31.550
Stop overthinking.

40:32.170 --> 40:33.710
I'll apply some more medicine for you.

40:49.370 --> 40:50.510
(Gray hair.)

40:53.010 --> 40:54.150
(It's her.)

40:55.290 --> 40:57.070
(It has always been her.)

40:58.290 --> 41:00.670
(She risked her life to save me
but refused to admit about it.)

41:01.370 --> 41:03.190
(Why is she avoiding acknowledging me?)

41:03.810 --> 41:05.830
(What kind of secret is she hiding?)

41:09.090 --> 41:10.670
These bloodstains are turning purple.

41:10.850 --> 41:12.510
They aimed to kill.

41:13.730 --> 41:15.070
The injury affects the internal organs.

41:16.210 --> 41:17.630
So the blood is naturally dark.

41:21.970 --> 41:23.430
What is the hour now?

41:23.650 --> 41:24.790
It's the Zi hour.

41:25.490 --> 41:27.110
I've been unconscious for six hours.

41:27.770 --> 41:29.670
I thought you would remain unconscious.

41:31.410 --> 41:32.609
I must return.

41:32.610 --> 41:34.470
How can you go back with such injuries?

41:34.610 --> 41:36.950
If they proceed to expel me
from the family registry,

41:37.250 --> 41:38.550
the family rules take precedence.

41:38.850 --> 41:40.910
His Majesty would also strip me
of my title as the heir

41:41.570 --> 41:42.950
and I would be in a hopeless situation.

41:43.850 --> 41:45.430
It's better to push forward
with determination

41:46.410 --> 41:47.710
than to hesitate.

41:47.850 --> 41:49.110
With such injuries,

41:49.330 --> 41:50.710
you'll need at least a month to recover.

41:51.370 --> 41:52.510
I can't afford to wait anymore.

41:53.850 --> 41:55.510
The guard's life is hanging by a thread,

41:55.970 --> 41:57.950
and my mother's just passed away.

41:59.770 --> 42:01.270
What I need the most

42:01.890 --> 42:03.510
is not to heal,

42:07.530 --> 42:09.150
but to be able to hold my weapon.

42:10.690 --> 42:13.670
(Duke of Ying's Residence)

42:43.010 --> 42:44.990
Fourth Young Lady has been punished
by Fifth Master Dou

42:45.010 --> 42:46.489
for meeting a man at night.

42:46.490 --> 42:47.489
That was me.

42:47.490 --> 42:48.770
- Your Lordship.
- Your Lordship.

42:49.130 --> 42:50.270
Fourth Young Lady,

42:50.490 --> 42:51.889
It was my reckless behavior

42:51.890 --> 42:53.670
and my disgraceful actions.

42:53.750 --> 42:55.489
Fourth Young Lady Dou
had nothing to do with it.

42:55.490 --> 42:56.710
So, Minister Dou,

42:57.130 --> 42:58.700
you can punish me instead.

43:02.370 --> 43:05.580
♪If dreams are shattered,
can they be whole again?♪

43:06.160 --> 43:09.740
♪If today brings hope, will it stay?♪

43:09.840 --> 43:15.740
♪Will the pain just weave
itself deeper?♪

43:15.770 --> 43:17.369
♪Where can this restless heart
find peace?♪

43:17.370 --> 43:20.449
♪Left alone in an empty hall♪

43:20.450 --> 43:24.310
♪A lifetime chasing fate's lonely call♪

43:24.400 --> 43:28.629
♪Watching seasons fade and storms rise♪

43:28.630 --> 43:31.199
♪It hurts but it's not all for nothing♪

43:31.200 --> 43:32.449
♪My heart is as empty as a quiet street♪

43:32.450 --> 43:35.489
♪Who cares about the path I walk alone?♪

43:35.490 --> 43:39.669
♪Would you take away
the weight of the past?♪

43:39.670 --> 43:41.649
♪Life is fleeting, like morning frost♪

43:41.650 --> 43:44.859
♪Even a moment feels endless with you♪

43:44.860 --> 43:51.000
♪Like a stream flowing steady
through time♪

43:52.970 --> 43:59.870
♪A lone flower falls from the eaves,
moonlight graces steps beneath♪

44:00.330 --> 44:07.550
♪Can anyone ease the pain of goodbye?♪

44:07.860 --> 44:11.070
♪If dreams are shattered,
can they be whole again?♪

44:11.650 --> 44:15.230
♪If today brings hope, will it stay?♪

44:15.330 --> 44:21.230
♪Will the pain just weave
itself deeper?♪

44:21.850 --> 44:23.129
♪In this chaotic world♪

44:23.130 --> 44:26.109
♪Only love lasts♪

44:26.110 --> 44:29.860
♪We'll get through
every challenge together♪

44:30.040 --> 44:34.269
♪No matter how cold
or uncertain the road♪

44:34.270 --> 44:36.849
♪There's nothing to fear
when I'm with you♪

44:36.850 --> 44:38.049
♪My heart feels empty♪

44:38.050 --> 44:40.979
♪But I can hear your voice♪

44:40.980 --> 44:45.259
♪In this life, under moonlight
and across the oceans♪

44:45.260 --> 44:47.700
♪We'll find our way back to each other♪

44:47.970 --> 44:48.929
(No animals were harmed
in the making of this drama)

44:48.930 --> 44:49.809
(Every medical behavior involved
and medicine used in the drama)

44:49.810 --> 44:50.769
(is required by the story.
Please don't try this at home)

44:50.770 --> 44:56.750
♪Together,
we'll make every moment count♪
